Slovenian Minister Bucan Resigns After Three Months on the Job

-- B y   B o r i s   C e r n i
-- 
2011-04-18T09:34:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/slovenian-minister-bucan-resigns-after-three-months-on-the-job.html
Slovenia’s Minister for Local
Government and Regional Development Dusa Trobec Bucan resigned
three months after taking the job, the ministry said.  “I can confirm she has tendered her resignation,” Marinka
Rojko, chief of staff at the  ministry  in Ljubljana said by phone
today. She declined to say why the minister stepped down.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Cerni in Ljubljana, Slovenia, at 
 bcerni@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  